{"id":233044,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-发课公司诉北京地税局一案将在朝阳法院/","date":"2012-06-19T17:01:08Z","modified":"2012-06-19T17:01:08Z","title":"维权网 | 发课公司诉北京地税局一案将在朝阳法院开庭","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div> </div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员亦然报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，北京市朝阳法院在未对发课公司调查取证申请、延期举证申请作出答复，发课公司法人代表路青未在场的情况下，将两份传票和合议庭人员告知书贴在北京草场地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">258</span><span>号门口，通知发课公司诉北京市地税局第二稽查局一案于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点</span><span>开庭。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>著名艺术家艾未未表示：政治案件经济处理。公安提前介入，公安、税务联合行动，先抓人再查账，程序严重违法。原告首次接到被告的《纳税检查通知书》为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，然在此之前，相关人员原告职员艾未未、文涛、胡明芬等已被公安机关关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>之后，公安机关又相继关押原告股东刘正刚、职员张劲松等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>上午，艾未未在首都国际机场出境前被警方带走后失踪，同日中午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>点，北京市公安局对位于朝阳区草场地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">258</span><span>号的艾未未住宅搜查了近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>个小时，扣押了电脑、移动硬盘、光盘、书籍等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">127</span><span>项物品，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>名艾未未工作室人员被警方带至南皋派出所询问至凌晨。随后，艾未未的助理文涛、发课公司员工刘正刚、胡明芬相继被绑架后失踪。期间所有失踪人员的家人没有收到任何法律文书，更不知亲人被羁押何处。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>艾未未于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>被以经济罪名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>取保候审</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>，随后被构陷受到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1522</span><span>万元的税务处罚。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，发课公司就涉税一案向北京朝阳法院提交</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>项申请</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、申调取被公安机关扣押的财务资料等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>项证据。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、申请刘正刚胡明芬出庭作证。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、申请第二稽查局尤鹏南等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>名人员出庭作证。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、申请延期举证。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>各界人士尤其是艾未未的“债主们”得知发课公司诉北京市地税局第二稽查局一案将于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点</span><span>开庭后，纷纷要求参与旁听，但法院的书记员却称旁听席位已满。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-3539150841687745217?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}